title: Sherlock Holmes With Carleton Hobbs - MP3 - Slimoo

Sherlock Holmes With Carleton Hobbs - Audio Drama - BBC7 
8 x 30 minute episodes - 128Kbps - Mp3 - Slimoo





Legendary radio actor Carleton Hobbs returned to the airwaves as the great detective for over 17 years. With Norman Shelley as Holmes's friend and companion Dr Watson, these extremely popular incarnations of the crime fighting duo are, to many people of a certain generation, the definitive renditions
